document_title: Obesity level 1: Causes, symptoms and treatment
subsection_content:
Includes 3 levels:
Obesity level 1: BMI from 30 to under 35.; Obesity level 2: BMI from 35 to less than 40.; Obesity level 3: BMI 40 or more (severe).
